855
00:59:36.527 --> 00:59:39.967
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It involves removing
the seizure-prone
part of the brain.</font>

856
00:59:39.998 --> 00:59:41.198
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

857
00:59:41.232 --> 00:59:43.032
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How will she be able
